data.description: Spacious home on just shy of 10 wooded acres. 3 bedrooms and 2 bath, split floor plan with attached 2 car garage. Just steps away there is a great space for an office or shop with an attached bedroom or office and half bath. Fight the summer month heat while avoiding the mosquitoes in your swimming pool located in the screened in porch! Great storage throughout the home, make your appointment today before it is too late! Home is zoned for Alto ISD.
